"10:70:6" : {s: 10, a: 70, w: 6, r: "رجع", t: "مَرْجِعُهُمْ", l: "مَرْجِع", lc: 16, tl: "marjiʿuhum", lb: "প্রত্যাবর্তনস্থল",e: "(is) their return", b: "তাদের প্রত্যাবর্তন", i: "tempat kembali mereka", f: 3, rm: "to return, turn back, turn off, (blame) upon any one, come back, repeat, answer, bring answer, be brought back. rajiun - one who returns. murjiun - return, termination. tarajaa (vb. 6)  -to return to one another."},
