"10:70:8" : {s: 10, a: 70, w: 8, r: "ذوق", t: "نُذِيقُهُمُ", l: "أَذَاقَ", lc: 22, tl: "nudhīquhumu", lb: "স্বাদ গ্রহণ করানো, আস্বাদন করানো",e: "We will make them taste", b: "তাদেরকে আস্বাদন করাব", i: "Kami rasakan kepada mereka", f: 1, rm: "to taste/experience/try/perceive. One who tastes, cause to taste."},
